### Get Admin Dashboard
GET {{BASE_URL}}/admin/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Get Hospital Units
GET {{BASE_URL}}/admin/unidades
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Create Hospital Unit
POST {{BASE_URL}}/admin/unidades
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

{
  "nome": "Unidade Centro",
  "endereco": {
    "logradouro": "Av. Paulista",
    "numero": "1000",
    "bairro": "Bela Vista",
    "cidade": "São Paulo",
    "estado": "SP",
    "cep": "01310100",
    "pais": "Brasil"
  },
  "telefone": "1133334444",
  "email": "centro@hospital.com",
  "capacidadeLeitos": 50
}

### Get Bed Details
GET {{BASE_URL}}/admin/leitos/detalhes
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Update Bed Status
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/admin/leitos/1/status
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

{
  "status": "OCUPADO",
  "pacienteId": 1,
  "dataOcupacao": "2025-08-31T08:00:00"
}

### Get Supplies
GET {{BASE_URL}}/admin/suprimentos
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Update Supply Stock
PUT {{BASE_URL}}/admin/suprimentos/1/estoque
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

{
  "quantidade": 100,
  "motivoAjuste": "Reposição de estoque",
  "funcionarioId": 1
}

### Get Financial Reports
GET {{BASE_URL}}/admin/relatorios/financeiro?dataInicio=2025-08-01&dataFim=2025-08-31
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}

### Get Appointment Statistics
GET {{BASE_URL}}/admin/relatorios/agendamentos?periodo=MENSAL&ano=2025&mes=8
Authorization: Bearer {{AUTH_TOKEN}}